1. *Piše* se da će doći poneki gost. (It is written that some guests will come.)
2. Ona *piše* pisma svom ocu svake nedelje. (She writes letters to her father every week.)
3. On *piše* knjigu o svojim putovanjima. (He is writing a book about his travels.)
4. *Pišu* se brojne knjige o pozorištu. (Many books are written about theatre.)
5. Ona *piše* svoju diplomsku radnju. (She is writing her thesis.)